text: Jacques Gaillard (born 16 August 1950) is a French ski jumper. He competed at the 1972 Winter Olympics and the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:French male ski jumpers Category:French male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
